==高十字架==
[[Image:Berkelysquarestatue.JPG|thumb]]
花园里的雕塑是布里斯托尔高十字架（High Cross）的复制品，原作立于1373年，以纪念英国各位君主，1733年搬到[[学院绿地_(布里斯托尔)|学院绿地]]。这座雕像于1768年搬到斯图黑德花园，今天可以看到。<ref>{{cite web|title=Stourhead: The Bristol High Cross |work=Follies and Monuments |url=http://www.follytowers.com/stourheadtrail1.html |accessdate=2007-05-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070501033006/http://www.follytowers.com/stourheadtrail1.html |archivedate=2007-05-01}}</ref> 目前的雕塑是一个复制品，最初位于[[学院绿地_(布里斯托尔)|学院绿地]],由约翰·诺顿创作于1851年，1940年代末被移除。布里斯托尔公民协会于1950年购买，立于伯克利广场。<ref>{{cite web|title=The High Cross |work=About Bristol |url=http://www.about-bristol.co.uk/old-04.asp |accessdate=2007-05-11|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20120717115635/http://www.about-bristol.co.uk/old-04.asp |archivedate=2012-07-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Bristol High Cross in east corner of Berkeley Square gardens|url=https://historicengland.org.uk/listing/the-list/list-entry/1202001|website=National Heritage List for England|publisher=Historic England|accessdate=9 September 2017|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027160936/https://historicengland.org.uk/listing/the-list/list-entry/1202001|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The First 50 years of the Bristol Civic Society |work=Bristol Civic Society |url=http://www.digitalbristol.org/members/civsoc/bcs/bcs.htm |accessdate=2007-05-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070219053824/http://www.digitalbristol.org/members/civsoc/bcs/bcs.htm |archivedate=2007-02-19}}</ref> 。

